# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:8
translate chinese loser_ending_e94592cd:

    # "I pick up a pizza, then go home and watch TV alone."
    "我买了一份披萨，然后回家独自看电视。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:11
translate chinese loser_ending_833bcf67:

    # "Then I watch some porn on the computer."
    "接着在电脑上看了些色情片。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:14
translate chinese loser_ending_e6e71336:

    # "I lie in bed that night and think about what the future might hold."
    "那天晚上，我躺在床上，思索着未来会怎样。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:17
translate chinese loser_ending_1b242190:

    # "I'll probably get a job in a lab somewhere."
    "我大概会在某个实验室找份工作。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:20
translate chinese loser_ending_4d4aa8f2:

    # "Maybe I'll find somebody to love one day."
    "也许有一天我会找到爱的人。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:21
translate chinese loser_ending_c3bf8e82:

    # "Maybe not."
    "也许不会。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:24
translate chinese loser_ending_9652d4a4:

    # "Maybe I'm too picky and nobody will ever be good enough for me."
    "也许我太挑剔了，根本找不到配得上我的人。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:27
translate chinese loser_ending_ec64b334:

    # "Maybe I'll go back to the other world."
    "也许我会回到另一个世界。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:30
translate chinese loser_ending_e3661b99:

    # "Maybe I'll live there with my mom and dad."
    "也许我会和爸爸妈妈一起生活在那里。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:33
translate chinese loser_ending_f982e9ec:

    # "Either way, I have to find a way to be happy."
    "无论怎样，我都得找到让自己快乐的方法。"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loserending.rpy:36
translate chinese loser_ending_b97a871d:

    # "What more could a person ask for?"
    "人还能奢求什么呢？"

